<section class="px-6 py-section sm:py-section-lg bg-white text-black">
  <div class="section-container text-center">
    <h2 class="section-title">Where we're headed</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      These are our next horizons. None of them exist yet — but this is the direction we're building toward.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-6 sm:gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card-light opacity-80">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm mb-4 font-mono">∞</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Always on, no hotkey.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          The assistant watches the game state silently and offers help when it senses you're stuck — no keypress needed.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-light opacity-80">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm mb-4 font-mono">⟳</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Real-time game awareness via mods.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Deep mod-based integration that tracks every NPC dialogue, quest update, and inventory change as they happen.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-light opacity-80">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm mb-4 font-mono">◈</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">One memory across every game.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          A persistent, portable memory layer that follows you from game to game — your choices, your discoveries, your context.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-light opacity-80">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm mb-4 font-mono">⇄</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Full-duplex, real-time interaction.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Speak naturally and hear responses aloud, just like talking to a co-pilot sitting next to you.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-light opacity-80 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm mb-4 font-mono">⎔</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Our own open model, on your device.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          A small, fine-tuned model that runs entirely offline — fast, private, purpose-built for gaming.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
